Original: <@RL,Seseri,00>あの レトルトレディとかって 人<CD><&BUF03>くん 知ってるの?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>(うっ...!)<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>あ あとのことは<CD>ぼくに まかせてください!<CF><D1>セセリさん 研究とかで<CD>いそがしいんでしょ?<CF><D1><@RL,Seseri,00>それは まあ...ね<CD>でも...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>ほ ほら ぼく ロボトルも<CD>じゅうぶん つよいし!<CF><D1><@RL,Seseri,00>そう?<CF><D1><@RL,Seseri,01>分かったわ おねがいするわね<CD>だけど あまリ むちゃしちゃダメよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>は-い!
Translated: <@RL,Seseri,00><&BUF03>, you know who that Lady Retort is?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>(Oops...!)<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>J-just leave the rest to me!<CF><D1>Seseri, aren't you busy with your research?<CF><D1><@RL,Seseri,00>Well... True, but...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>R-right? I'm plenty strong in Robattles!<CF><D1><@RL,Seseri,00>Is that so?<CF><D1><@RL,Seseri,01>Alright, I'm leaving it to you. But, don't be rash, okay?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Okay~!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>あぶないなぁ キララさん...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>さてと 手がかリは ないし<CD>もういちど セレクトしぶに<CF><D1>行ってみようかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>Ms. Kirara, that was so close...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Well, can't do anything without clues. Should I go to Select Branch one more time?

Original: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,00>たいいんの ほうこくを<CD>まっているで あリます
Translated: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,00>I'm waiting for reports from the troops.

Original: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,00>メダルはつ電所からは<CD>まだ みかいしゅうで あリました<CF><D1>「ノ-ス」メダルが<CD>うばわれた もようで あリます!<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>ふははははは!
Translated: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,00>Things haven't been retrieved from the Medal Power Plant.<CF><D1>It seems that <f02>North<f00> Medal has been stolen!<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>Fuahahahahaha!

Original: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,03>くせ者で あリます!
Translated: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,03>You knave!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>ぼくも 行こう!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>Let's go!

Original: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,00>快盗レトルト...あなどれない<CD>やつで あリます!
Translated: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,00>Phantom Retort... He's not an ordinary thief!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>えっと-...
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Um...

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>ふはははは!<CF><D1><@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,03>まつで あリますっ!!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>わ-!<CF><D1><@RL,Lady2,00>きゃ-っ!!
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>Fuahahahaha!<CF><D1><@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,03>Hold it right there!!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>Woah!<CF><D1><@RL,Lady2,00>Kyaah!!

Original: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,00>にげられたで あリます...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>ええぇ-?
Translated: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,00>He got away...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Eeeh?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>レトルトさん どこ<CD>行っちゃったのかなぁ?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>Where did Phantom Retort go?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>何だろう? これ<CD>えっとぉ...<CF><D1>「<&BUF03>くん<CD>きみが この てがみを<CF><D1>よむ時には わたしは もう<CD>この町には いないだろう<CF><D1>海の そこまでも おいかけて<CD>来るがいい...快盗レトルト」<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>レトルトさんからの<CD>ちょうせんじょうだ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>「海の そこまでも」...か<CD>よぉし! つかまえて みせるぞ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>What's this? Let's see...<CF><D1>"<&BUF03>, if you're reading this letter, I'm probably not in this town anymore.<CF><D1>Feel free to chase me to depths of the ocean... Signed, Phantom Retort."<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>It's a challenge from Phantom Retort!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>"To the depths of the ocean"... Alright! I'm gonna catch him for sure!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>いずみの 中心に 新しい ぞうが<CD>おかれてる<CF><D1>「魚人のぞう」って いうのか<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>...あんまリ うれしく ないなぁ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>There's a new statue at the center of the fountain.<CF><D1>A<f02> Fishman Statue<f00>?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>...That doesn't really make me happy.

Original: <@RL,Lady2,00>♥スト-ングッズは<CD>女の子に 大人気よ
Translated: <@RL,Lady2,00>♥ Stone souvenirs are a big hit among the girls.

Original: <@RL,Lady2,00>「金魚のぞう」が なくなって<CD>かわリに おかれたのが<CF><D1>うつくしくもない「魚人のぞう」よ!<CD>...ひどい 話だわ!
Translated: <@RL,Lady2,00>After the <f02>Goldfish Statue<f00> went missing, it was replaced by an ugly <f02>Fishman Statue<f00>!<CF><D1>...This isn't a joke!

Original: <@RL,Girl2,00>こいうらないの しんでんには<CD>こいの ようせいが すんでるんだって
Translated: <@RL,Girl2,00>In the Love Divination shrine, there lives the Love Fairy... or so I heard.

Original: <@RL,Milky,02>はぁ-い わたしは こいの<CD>ようせい ミルキ-ちゃんで-す!<CF><D1><@RL,Milky,00>ん-- 今の キミは...<CF><D1><@RL,Milky,01>しんけんロボトルが こううんを<CD>よぶでしょう!
Translated: <@RL,Milky,02>Hello~ I'm Milky the Love Fairy~!<CF><D1><@RL,Milky,00>Hm... At this moment...<CF><D1><@RL,Milky,01>Good fortune will come to you after a serious Robattle!

Original: <@RL,Milky,02>キミの 勝ちぃ!<CD>それじゃ これを あげる♥
Translated: <@RL,Milky,02>You won! This is for you~♥

Original: <@RL,Milky,00>え? ゲ-ムに かんけいないから<CD>あんまし うれしくない?<CF><D1>でも 当たれば ラッキ-♥<CD>4つあつめて おうぼしてみてね<CF><D1><@RL,Milky,02>それじゃ まったね-♥
Translated: <@RL,Milky,00>Eh? You don't really want it since it has nothing to do with the game?<CF><D1>But, you'll get something if you're lucky~♥<D3>Try entering the raffle once you gather 4 of them.<CF><D1><@RL,Milky,02>See you again~♥

Original: <@RL,Milky,02>ちょっと いどうしてみました<CF><D1><@RL,Milky,01>ロボトルしよっか
Translated: <@RL,Milky,02>I tried changing locations.<CF><D1><@RL,Milky,01>Let's Robattle.

Original: <@RL,Milky,02>それじゃ まったね-♥
Translated: <@RL,Milky,02>See you again~♥

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ん? 何か おちてるぞ?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Hm? There's something on the ground.

Original: <@RL,Milky,02>かわいい まじょの ミルキ-が<CD>なやめる キミに こいの<CF><D1>お.ま.じ.な.い♥
Translated: <@RL,Milky,02>If you're feeling apprehensive, the cute witch Milky is here to give you...<CF><D1>A. Love. Charm~♥

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ロボトルが おまじない...?<CF><D1><@RL,Milky,01>きくと 思えば きくものよ<CD>かぜぐすリと いっしょね<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>「こい」と「かぜ」って<CD>にてるのかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>So, Robattle is your idea of a good luck charm?<CF><D1><@RL,Milky,01>It's like a cold medicine. If you think that it works, then it will.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Is "love" similar to a "cold"?

Original: <@RL,Milky,01>キミの たたかい方で<CD>心に ひめた 思いが 分かるのよ♥
Translated: <@RL,Milky,01>I can tell the hidden feelings in your heart from the way you fight~♥

Original: <@RL,Milky,02>ふ-ん な-るほどね-♥
Translated: <@RL,Milky,02>Hm~ I see~♥

Original: <@RL,Girl2,00>ステキな こいの おまもリ<CD>♥スト-ンの ネックレスは<CF><D1>あの! 何年も ケンカが つづいてた<CD>マ-メイド学底と マ-マン学底を<CF><D1>みごと なかなおリ させました!<CD>おきゃくさん 買ってってぇ-♥
Translated: <@RL,Girl2,00>With this wonderful ♥ stone necklace... would you believe it!<CF><D1>This love charm made the Mermaid and Merman students reconcile after their years-long fight!<CF><D1>Buy some while they're still in stock~♥

Original: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>ワタシが 作って 売ってる<CD>魚人の キ-ホルダ-は<CF><D1>どうして 売れないんでしょ?<CD>こんなに かわいいのに...
Translated: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>I wonder why the fishman keychains that I made aren't selling at all.<CF><D1>I mean, look at how cute they are.

Original: <@RL,Girl2,00>ふぁ-あ 店番って たいくつ-!<CD>かえろっかな-
Translated: <@RL,Girl2,00><f02>Yawn<f00>... Tending the store is so boring! Maybe I'll just go home.

Original: <@RL,BipedMedabot,00>おきゃくさん あっての<CD>しょうばいや!<CF><D1>どんどん 貝てってや!<CD>ベんきょう しまっせ!
Translated: <@RL,BipedMedabot,00>I'm operatin' a customer-oriented business here!<CF><D1>Keep on buyin'! I'll give ya a discount!

Original: <@RL,Lady2,00>海てい いせきから はっくつされる<CD>きれいな 石は どれを とっても<CF><D1>コレクションの かち あリよ!<CD>おみやげに お1つ いかが?
Translated: <@RL,Lady2,00>These beautiful stones were excavated from the deep-sea ruins.<CF><D1>Each of them will make quite the collection! Would you like one as a souvenir?

Original: <@RL,Lady2,00>おみやげに こいの ほうせきは<CD>いかが?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>いくらですか?<CF><D1><@RL,Lady2,00>10000¥よ♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>(た 高い...)<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>どうしよっかな?<*04>
Translated: <@RL,Lady2,00>Would you like to buy a love jewel as a souvenir?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>How much is it?<CF><D1><@RL,Lady2,00>It's ¥10,000 ♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>(T-that's expensive...)<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>What should I do?<*04>

Original: <@RL,Lady2,00>それ さいごの 1こだったの<CD>ラッキ-ね♥
Translated: <@RL,Lady2,00>That was the last one, you know? Lucky you~♥

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>お金が 足リないや...
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>I don't have enough money...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>やめとこっと
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Maybe not.

Original: <@RL,Lady2,00>おみやげものの 中では やっぱリ<CD>♥スト-ングッズが 1番の<CF><D1>売れすじよ
Translated: <@RL,Lady2,00>Stone goods are the best selling souvenirs ♥

Original: <@RL,Lady2,00>あの「魚人のぞう」はね<CF><D1>海てい いせきから<CD>はっくつされた ものなの
Translated: <@RL,Lady2,00>Did you know? The <f02>Fishman Statue<f00> was excavated from the deep-sea ruins.

Original: <@RL,Rintarou,00>ヒカルさんは どこだぜ?
Translated: <@RL,Rintarou,00>Where's Hikaru?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>あれ? きみ なんで ここに?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Huh? What are you doing here?

Original: <@RL,Rintarou,00>ヒカルさんを さがしてるだぜ!
Translated: <@RL,Rintarou,00>I'm looking for Hikaru!

Original: <@RL,Rintarou,00>ほかを さがすだぜ!
Translated: <@RL,Rintarou,00>I'll go look somewhere else!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>元気だなぁ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>He's so full of energy.

Original: <@RL,Boy3,00>この前 おれたちが 使わせて<CD>もらったから 今日は 使ってくれよ<CF><D1><@RL,Girl2,00>そんな...わるいわ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>すっかリ なかよしなんだなぁ
Translated: <@RL,Boy3,00>We already got to use it last time, so go ahead and don't worry about us.<CF><D1><@RL,Girl2,00>But... that'd make us feel bad.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>They're totally good friends now.

Original: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>...でね-!<CF><D1><@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>えぇ- ほんとぉ?
Translated: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>...You see!<CF><D1><@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>Eeh? Really?

Original: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>もうすぐ 海中林で<CD>いせき はっくつするんだよ!
Translated: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>We're going to excavate the ruins in the Undersea Forest!

Original: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>海中林で これから 海てい いせきの<CD>はっくつを するんだよ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>はっくつ?
Translated: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>We're on our way to excavate the deep-sea ruins in the Undersea Forest!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Excavate?

Original: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>うん! 「金魚のぞう」とか<CD>ハ-トスト-ンとかも 海中林で<CF><D1>貝つかったんだよ!<CD>メダルや パ-ツとかも<CF><D1>けっこ- 貝つかるんだ-!<CD>ねっ いっしょに 行かない?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>え? いいのかなぁ?<CF><D1><@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>い-って い-って!<CD>今なら 行けるから! 行こ!
Translated: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>Mmhmm! <f02>Goldfish Statue<f00>, heart stones, they're all found in the Undersea Forest!<CF><D1>There are Medals and Parts, too! Say, want to go with us?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Eh? Can I?<CF><D1><@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>Of course you can! This is your chance! Let's go!

Original: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>海中林は 立ち入リきんし!
Translated: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>No entry to the Undersea Forest!

Original: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>あぶないから 入っちゃダメ!
Translated: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>You can't go in there! It's dangerous.

Original: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>え-ん はっくつ げんばに 行ったら<CD>おい出されちゃった-!
Translated: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>Boo hoo... I got kicked out from the excavation site!

Original: <@RL,Sailor,00>はっくつは きけんな さぎょうだ!<CD>あっちヘ 行ってるんだ!
Translated: <@RL,Sailor,00>Excavation is dangerous work! You should go away!

Original: <@RL,Sailor,00>ほらほら! さぎょうの じゃまだ!<CD>子どもは あっちヘ 行った!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>がっかリ
Translated: <@RL,Sailor,00>Hey! You're in the way! Children shouldn't be here!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>Bummer.

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>ふはははは!
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>Fuahahahaha!

Original: <@RL,Sailor,00>なっ! だれだ!<CD>どこから わいて出たっ!?<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>この かっこうでは さっぱリだが<CD>快盗レトルト ただ今 さんじょう!
Translated: <@RL,Sailor,00>Who's there!? How did you get here!?<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>Although I'm not in my best attire, Phantom Retort has arrived!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>レトルトさん!?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Phantom Retort!?

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>メダルは このレトルトが お先に<CD>はっくつ させてもらった!<CF><D1>もう ここに メダルは のこって<CD>いない! ざんねんだったな<CF><D1>さらばだ ふはははは!
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>This Medal is mine to excavate!<CF><D1>Unfortunately, there are no more Medals to be found here!<CF><D1>Farewell! Fuahahahaha!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>そんなっ! レトルトさん!<CF><D1><@RL,Sailor,00>はっくつは 中止だ!<CD>セレクト隊に つうほうだ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>No way! Phantom Retort!<CF><D1><@RL,Sailor,00>Stop excavating! We need to report this to the Select Corp!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>あわわわ 大変なことに<CD>なっちゃった!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>Awawawa... Things have gotten out of hand!

Original: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>みんな かえっちゃったよぉ<CD>どうして?
Translated: <@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>Everyone's gone. Why?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>はっくつが 中止に なったんだ<CF><D1><@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>ふ-ん そうなんだ-<CD>きっと ボクを おいかえした<CF><D1>バツだね!<CD>じゃ ボクも かえろ-っと!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>The excavation has been suspended.<CF><D1><@RL,SwimmingMedabot,00>I see~ It must be their divine punishment for chasing me away!<CF><D1>I'm going back as well!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>メダルが おちてる<CD>あれ? このメダル たしか<CF><D1>レトルトさんに うばわれたっていう<CD>「ノ-ス」メダル...?<CF><D1>...と いうことは?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>There's a Medal on the ground. Huh? Isn't this <f02>North<f00> Medal? The one that Phantom Retort stole?<CF><D1>Which means...

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>ふははははは!<CD>よくぞ 貝つけた!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>え? え?
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>Fuahahahahaha! Well done finding that!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Eh? Huh?

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,02>よいしょ よいしょ
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,02>Hup, hup.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>レトルトさん!<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>やくそくだったね<CD><&BUF03>くん<CF><D1>わたしを さがしだした きみとの<CD>ロボトル!<CF><D1>では その メダルを かけて<CD>しょうぶだ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Phantom Retort!<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>We made a promise, didn't we? <&BUF03>.<CF><D1>That if you managed to find me, I would Robattle with you!<CF><D1>Well then, that Medal will be the wager of this fight!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>貝たことのない メダロットだ!<CD>これって...カブト?<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>カブトの中の カブト!<CD>ヘラクレス大カブト型 メダロット<CF><D1>「ア-クビ-トル」だ!<CD>はたして きみに 勝てるかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>I've never seen that Medarot before! Is that... a Kabuto?<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>It's the Kabuto among Kabuto! <f02>Arcbeetle<f00> is the Hercules Bettle Medarot!<CF><D1>Can he win against you, I wonder?

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>みごとだ <&BUF03>くん!<CD>さあ その メダルを<CF><D1>うけとるが いい<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>えっ でも これって...<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>それは 元々 ロボロボ団によって<CD>いほうに はっくつされた メダルだ<CF><D1>...ざんねんながら レアメダルじゃ<CD>なかったけどね<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>レアメダルを さがして?<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>はかせが きみから レアメダルや<CD>マザ-メダロットの 話を 聞いて<CF><D1>ぼくに レアメダルの かいしゅうを<CD>いそがせたんだ<CF><D1>わるものの 手に わたったら<CD>大変だからね<CF><D1><@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,00>レトルトは こっちに<CD>にげたで あリます!<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>おっと うるさいやつらが 来た
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>Splendid, <&BUF03>! That Medal is yours.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Eh? Isn't this...<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>It was illegally excavated by the RoboRobo Gang.<CF><D1>...Unfortunately, it wasn't a rare Medal by any means.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Why are you looking for rare Medals?<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>After hearing about rare Medals and Mother Medarot from you, Professor hurried me to retrieve rare Medals.<CF><D1>It would've been a mess if a bad guy happens to obtain them.<CF><D1><@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,00>Phantom Retort ran towards this area!<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>Whoops, the noisy bunch is here.

Original: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,02>快盗レトルト!<CD>貝つけたで あリます!
Translated: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,02>It's Phantom Retort! He's here!

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>また 会おう!<CD>さらばだ! ふははははははは!!
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>We'll meet again! Farewell! Fuahahahahahahaha!!

Original: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,02>ずるいで あリます!
Translated: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,02>That's cheating!

Original: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,02>お おいかけるで あリます!
Translated: <@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,02>A-after him!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,01>レトルトさん かっこいい!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,01>Phantom Retort is so cool!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>そうそう この メダル<CD>持って 行かなきゃ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Oh yeah, I need to take this Medal with me.

Original: <@RL,Rintarou,00>ヒカルさんは どこだぜ?
Translated: <@RL,Rintarou,00>Where's Hikaru?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>すごいね きみ! こんな所まで<CD>どうやって 来たの?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Wow, how did you even get here?

Original: <@RL,Rintarou,00>ヒカルさんを さがしてるだぜ!
Translated: <@RL,Rintarou,00>I'm looking for Hikaru!

Original: <@RL,Rintarou,00>ほかを さがすだぜ!
Translated: <@RL,Rintarou,00>I'll go look somewhere else!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>たまには ぼくの話も<CD>聞いてよ-
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>Would it hurt for him to talk with me?

Original: <@RL,Girl2,00>ここは あたしら シ-フェアリ-ズの<CD>きょうしつよ!
Translated: <@RL,Girl2,00>This is the Sea Fairies' classroom!

Original: <@RL,Girl2,00>マ-マンの 子たち 早く<CD>つよく なってくれないかな-?<CF><D1>じゃないと ロボトルしたって<CD>つまんないし
Translated: <@RL,Girl2,00>I wonder if the Merman boys can't hurry and get stronger.<CF><D1>Otherwise, it won't be any bit fun Robattling them.

Original: <@RL,Girl2,00>やっぱし シ-フェアリ-ズの<CD>リ-ダ-は ウオナさましか<CF><D1>いないわよ-!
Translated: <@RL,Girl2,00>Miss Uona is the one and only leader of the Sea Fairies!

Original: <@RL,Girl2,00>来たわね まってたわよ<CD>あたしたちと しょうぶなさい!
Translated: <@RL,Girl2,00>Finally here, aren't you? We've been waiting. Fight us!

Original: <@RL,Girl2,00>どう? あたしたちも けっこう<CD>院を 上げたでしょ?<CF><D1>また あそんでよ!
Translated: <@RL,Girl2,00>How was it? We've gotten stronger too, right?<CF><D1>Come play with us again!

Original: <@RL,Boy3,00>ウオナちゃん...<CD>たたかう きみは ステキだ♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>ラブレタ-男...?
Translated: <@RL,Boy3,00>Uona... You're so gallant when you fight~♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>The love-letter guy...?

Original: <@RL,Boy3,00>みんな がんばれ-
Translated: <@RL,Boy3,00>You can do it, guys!

Original: <@RL,Boy3,00>よくぞ 来てくれましたね 先生!<CF><D1>しゅぎょうを かさね つよくなった<CD>おしえ子の すがたを 貝てください!
Translated: <@RL,Boy3,00>Thank you very much for coming, teacher!<CF><D1>Please witness how strong I've gotten after all those trainings!

Original: <@RL,Boy3,00>どうです? 先生!?
Translated: <@RL,Boy3,00>What do you think? Teacher!
<@RL,Boy3,00>...Heh.

Original: <@RL,Boy3,00>「フッ」って 何だよ!<CD>「フッ」って!! お前っ!!
Translated: <@RL,Boy3,00>Hey! Did you just snort at me!?

Original: <@RL,Boy3,00>がんばれば がんばれば<CD>いつかは いつかは<CF><D1>女の子にも 勝てるようになる!
Translated: <@RL,Boy3,00>If I keep going at it without giving up, someday...<CF><D1>I'll become strong enough to win against the girls!

Original: <@RL,Boy3,00>「えがおで ロボトル<CD>シ-ドラゴンズ!」<CF><D1>キャッチフレ-ズは こんな<CD>かんじかな?
Translated: <@RL,Boy3,00>"Robattle with smiles! Sea Dragons!"<CF><D1>Does that work as a catchphrase?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>あ キララさんだ!<CD>やっぱリ かえってたんですね!<CF><D1><@RL,Kirara,01>じゅ-ぶん あそんだしね!<CD>...と いうわけで<CF><D1><&BUF03>くんには<CD>がんばった ごほうびに いいこと<CF><D1>おしえたげる♥<CD>パスワ-ドは「き」よ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>...は?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Oh, it's Ms. Kirara! So you've returned!<CF><D1><@RL,Kirara,01>I've gotten my fill of fun! Anyway...<CF><D1><&BUF03>, since you've been working so hard, I'll tell you something good~♥<CF><D1>The password is "Ki".<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>...Huh?

Original: <@RL,Kirara,01>パスワ-ドを あつめて おうぼしてね<CD>きかんないに よ.ろ.し.く♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>あの- キララさん<CD>だれにむかって 話してるんですか?
Translated: <@RL,Kirara,01>Gather the password and enter the raffle. There's a time limit, though~♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Um, Ms. Kirara? Who are you talking to?

Original: <@RL,Kirara,01>あたると いいわね♥
Translated: <@RL,Kirara,01>I hope you'll get lucky~♥

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>ただ今 ユウキおぼっちゃまは<CD>おるすで ございます
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Young master Yuki is away at the moment.

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>これはこれは <CD>いらっしゃいませ
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Oh my, welcome.

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>ユウキおぼっちゃまからは<CD>スイデンジさまの おたくヘ<CF><D1>おでかけすると うかがっておリます
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Young master Yuki mentioned that he was going to Swedenji's residence.

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>ユウキおぼっちゃまですか?<CD>何でも ホテルで どなたかとの<CF><D1>おやくそくが あるとか...
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Young master Yuki? I was told that he was meeting someone at the hotel.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>カギが かかってる
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>It's locked.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>クマ型メダロット「ベティベア」!<CD>はじめて 貝た!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>It's Betty Bear, a Bear Medarot! This is my first time seeing one!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>クマ型メダロット「チャ-リ-ベア」!<CD>はじめて 貝た!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>It's Charlie Bear, a Bear Medarot! This is my first time seeing one!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>マスコット型メダロット「ラピ」!<CD>...これは 知ってる!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>It's Rappy, a Mascot Medarot! ...I know this one!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>「クマ」の メダルだって!<CD>はじめて 貝た!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>It's <f02>Bear<f00> Medal! This is my first time seeing one!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>「ト-タス」の メダルだって!<CD>はじめて 貝た!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>It's <f02>Tortoise <f00>Medal! This is my first time seeing one!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>うどんの しるは クリ-ムシチュ-!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>これは...いいかも しれない
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>The udon's broth is cream stew!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>This... might actually be good.

Original: <@RL,Lady,00>今夜の メニュ-は<CD>クリ-ムシチュ-うどん<CF><D1>ブルゴ-ニュ風よ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>!!<CD>...きょうみ ある!
Translated: <@RL,Lady,00>Tonight's menu is cream stew udon, Bourgogne-style.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>!! ...I'm so interested!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>あの...
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Um...

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>これは これは<CD>おはつに お目に かかリます<CF><D1>わたくし パディおじょうさまの<CD>しつじで ございます<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>あ はい パディさんの<CD>ヒツジさんですね はじめまして<CF><D1>ところで 何を やっていたんですか?<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>これは おはずかしいところを<CD>お目に かけました<CF><D1>インタ-ネットたからくじで<CD>ございます<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>たからくじ?<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>はい これが 毎月の わたくしの<CD>楽しみで ございまして<CF><D1>あなたさまは たからくじに<CD>きょうみは おあリですか?<*04>
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Oh my, I believe this is our first time meeting.<CF><D1>I'm mistress Paddy's butler.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Oh hello, so you're Paddy's butter. Nice to meet you.<CF><D1>By the way, what are you doing?<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>That was embarrassing.<CF><D1>I'm participating in an online lottery.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Lottery?<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>Yes, this is my monthly pleasure.<CF><D1>Do you have any interest in lotteries?<*04>

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>そうですか! では お近づきの<CD>しるしに これを おうけとリください
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Really!? Then please take this from the mark nearby.

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>まぁまぁ そうおっしゃらずに!<CD>これを おうけとリください
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Now, now, don't be shy! Please take this.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>これは?<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>何でも それを 4つ あつめて<CD>きげんないに イマジニアという<CF><D1>会社に 送リますと<CD>ごうか けいひんが 当たるかも<CF><D1>しれないという ものです<CD>送ってみては いかがですかな?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>はぁ...あリがとうございます
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>What's this?<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>I was told that if you manage to gather all 4 of them, you can send them to a company called Imagineer for a chance to win wonderful prizes.<CF><D1>Would you like to try?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>I see... Thank you for telling me.

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>う-ん なかなかですなぁ...
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Hm... Now that was something...

Original: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>ベティ やっておしまい!
Translated: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>Do it, Betty!

Original: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>つめが あまいですわね!
Translated: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>Your finishing is weak!

Original: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>ユウキちゃんと わたくしのなかを<CD>じゃますると ゆるしませんことよ!
Translated: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>Get in between Yuki and I, and you'll regret it!

Original: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>早く あっちに 行っておしまい!
Translated: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>Just go away already!

Original: <@RL,Mascot,00>ピ-!
Translated: <@RL,Mascot,00>Pii!

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>キミと ボクは うんめいの<CD>赤い いとで むすばれて いるのさ<CF><D1><@RL,LittleGirl,00>ユウキちゃん...♥
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>You and I are connected by the red thread of fate.<CF><D1><@RL,LittleGirl,00>Oh Yuki...♥

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>あ! ユウキさん!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Oh, Yuki!

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>やあ <&BUF03>くん<CD>今 ボクは ハニ-と<CF><D1>あいを かたリ合って いたのさ<CF><D1><@RL,LittleGirl,00>こっちに来て ちゃんと あいさつ<CD>しなさいっ!
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Hey, <&BUF03>. Honey and I are reaffirming our love right now.<CF><D1><@RL,LittleGirl,00>Get over here and greet me properly!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>あ はい
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>O-okay.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>は はじめまして ハニ-さん<CF><D1><@RL,LittleGirl,00>いやですわ わたくしの 名前は<CD>ハニ-では あリませんことよ!<CF><D1>わたくしは ユウキちゃんの<CD>いいなずけの パディちゃんですわ<CF><D1>それから この子が ベティ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>H-hello, Ms. Honey.<CF><D1><@RL,LittleGirl,00>Geez! My name isn't 'Honey'!<CF><D1>I'm Paddy, Yuki's fiancee.<CF><D1>And this one is Betty.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>か かわいい ピ-ちゃんですね<CF><D1><@RL,LittleGirl,01>ピ-ちゃんじゃ あリませんわ!<CD>ベティですわ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>T-that's a cute Pii.<CF><D1><@RL,LittleGirl,01>He's not Pii! He's Betty!

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>はっはっは なかなか たのしかったよ<CF><D1>それじゃ ボクは そろそろ<CD>しつれいするよ アデュ-!
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Ha ha ha! I had a good time.<CF><D1>It's about time for me to go. Adieu!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>あ! ユウキさん!<CD>ちょっと まっ...<CF><D1><@RL,LittleGirl,01>まだ お話は おわってませんことよ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>Oh, Yuki! Wait--<CF><D1><@RL,LittleGirl,01>I haven't finished talking!

Original: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>どう? まいリましたこと?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>(ひ-っ この人 何か ヤバイ!)<CD>さっ さよならっ!!
Translated: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>So? Do you admit defeat?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>(Hiih! This girl feels like bad news!) B-buh bye!

Original: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>あっ! おまちなさい!
Translated: <@RL,LittleGirl,01>Hey, wait!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>ユウキさんの いいなずけって<CD>すごい人だなぁ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>それにしても ユウキさん<CD>どこ 行っちゃったんだろ?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>Yuki's fiancee is amazing.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Anyway, I wonder where he went.

Original: <@RL,Lady2,00>あなたって 本当に<CD>わるい人ね♥
Translated: <@RL,Lady2,00>You're such a bad boy~♥

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>ああハニ- キミの ひとみは<CD>まるで メダリアの かがやき...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>ゆ ユウキさん...?
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Oh honey, your eyes shine like a Medalia...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Y-Yuki...?

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>やあ <&BUF03>くん<CD>今 ハニ-と あいを<CF><D1>かたらっていたんだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>ハニ-さんって<CD>たくさんいる ものなんですか?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>ボクにとっては 全せかいの<CD>じょせいが ハニ-なのさ!<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>ところで ボクに 何か用かい?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>メダロットはかせに 聞いたんです<CF><D1>今 ブラックカブトの メダルって<CD>ユウキさんが 持ってるんですか?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>ああ あずかってるよ<CD>あれは 元々 キミの なんだってね<CF><D1>ボクの家に おいで<CD>面白いものを 貝せてあげよう
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Hey, <&BUF03>. Honey and I are reaffirming our love right now.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Just how many Ms. Honeys are there?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>All women in this world are my honey!<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>So, do you need something from me?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>I heard from Dr. Medarot.<CF><D1>Do you have the Black Kabuto Medal with you?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Yeah, I was asked to hold on to it. I heard that it's yours.<CF><D1>Come over to my home, I have something interesting to show you.

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>やあ <&BUF03>くん<CD>今 ハニ-と あいを<CF><D1>かたらっていたんだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>ハニ-さんって<CD>たくさんいる ものなんですか?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>ボクにとっては 全せかいの<CD>じょせいが ハニ-なのさ!<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>ところで ボクに 何か用かい?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>メダロットはかせに 聞いたんです<CF><D1>今 ブラッククワガタの メダルって<CD>ユウキさんが 持ってるんですか?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>ああ あずかってるよ<CD>あれは 元々 キミの なんだってね<CF><D1>ボクの家に おいで<CD>面白いものを 貝せてあげよう
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Hey, <&BUF03>. Honey and I are reaffirming our love right now.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Just how many Ms. Honey is there?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>All women in this world are my honey!<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>So, do you need something from me?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>I heard from Dr. Medarot.<CF><D1>Do you have the Black Kugawata Medal with you?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Yeah, I was asked to hold on to it. I heard that it's yours.<CF><D1>Come over to my home, I have something interesting to show you.

Original: <@RL,Lady2,00>もう! 何かあると いつも<CD>すぐ かえっちゃうんだから!
Translated: <@RL,Lady2,00>Geez! He always goes right off whenever something comes up!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>あ ご ごめんなさいっ<CF><D1><@RL,Lady2,00>しつれい しちゃうわ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>Oh, s-sorry.<CF><D1><@RL,Lady2,00>If you will excuse me!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>今のって<CD>ぼくのせい...なのかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>Was that... my fault?

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>今 ブラックカブトメダルを 使って<CD>テストバトルを していたんだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>そんなっ! きけんですよ!<CD>ブラックカブトは...!<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>「メダロット3げんそく」が<CD>ないって 言うんだろ?<CF><D1>じゃ ためして みるか
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>I'm currently doing test battles with the Black Kabuto Medal.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>No way! That's dangerous! The Black Kabuto isn't--<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>It's not restricted by the Three Laws of Medarobotics, right?<CF><D1>Let's try it out then.

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>今 ブラッククワガタメダルを 使って<CD>テストバトルを していたんだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>そんなっ! きけんですよ!<CD>ブラッククワガタは...!<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>「メダロット3げんそく」が<CD>ないって 言うんだろ?<CF><D1>じゃ ためして みるか
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>I'm currently doing test battles with the Black Kuwagata Medal.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>No way! That's dangerous! The Black Kuwagata isn't--<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>It's not restricted by the <f02>Three Laws of Medarobotics<f00>, right?<CF><D1>Let's try it out then.

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>ブラックビ-トル!
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>Black Beetle!

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>ブラックスタッグ!
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>Black Stag!

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00><&BUF03>くんを やっつけろ!
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>Attack <&BUF03>!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>ぎっ!?!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Gh!

Original: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>できま...せん<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>あれ?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>ふしぎだろ? この間までは<CD>たしかに そのメダルには<CF><D1>「メダロット3げんそく」が<CD>かけていたのに<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>あ! そうか ブラックデビルの<CD>えいきょうが なくなって...!<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>ふっ キミには じじょうが<CD>分かっているようだ<CF><D1>じゃあ せきにんを 持って<CD>そのメダルを あずかって もらうよ
Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>I... can't.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Huh?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,00>Strange, isn't it? This Medal didn't have the <f02>Three Laws of Medarobotics<f00> before.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Oh, I see! Black Devil's influence is gone!<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Hmph, it seems you get the gist.<CF><D1>Take responsibility and take a good care of it.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>え! 本当ですか!?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>ああ 本当さ<CD>だけど その前に<CF><D1>せっかくだから お手合わせ<CD>ねがおうかな?<CF><D1>ステ-ジに 上がってくれたまえ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Eh? Are you sure!?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Yeah, I'm sure. But before that, can you go for a round with me?<CF><D1>Get on the stage!

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>じゃあ 行くよ!
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Here I go!

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>さすがだね キミは<CD>おそれいったよ!
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Impressive. Very impressive!

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>はい うけとって
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Here, take it.

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>そうそう パ-ツもね
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Oh yeah. Take the Parts, too.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>...?<CD>あの- メダルの方は ぼくが<CF><D1>はかせに あずけたんで<CD>分かるんですけど<CF><D1>パ-ツは どうやって<CD>手に入れたんですか?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>手に 入れたんじゃない<CD>作ったんだ<CF><D1>わが メダロット社が ほこる<CD>「ドリ-ム.マシ-ン」でね<CF><D1>メダルに 1番 合う パ-ツを<CD>こうあんしたら この 形に<CF><D1>なったんだよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>ヘえ...<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>それじゃ ボクは ハニ-との<CD>やくそくが あるからね!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>さっきの人ですか?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>ごそうぞうに おまかせするよ<CD>それじゃあ アデュ-!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>...? I know that the professor asked you to hold on to the medal.<CF><D1>Although, where did you get the Parts from?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>I didn't 'get' them.<CF><D1>I made them with the <f02>Dream Machine<f00>, Medarot Corporation's masterpiece.<CF><D1>This is what came out when I wanted to make the most suitable Parts for this Medal.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>Wow...<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Well then, I'm meeting my honey after this! So...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Is it the girl from earlier?<CF><D1><@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>I'll leave it to your imagination. Well then, adieu!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>(いいのかな-...?)
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>(Is this really okay...?)

Original: <@RL,Lady3,00>さいきんさ- 変わったわよね<CD>カラスくん
Translated: <@RL,Lady3,00>Crow has changed recently.

Original: <@RL,Lady3,00>そ-そ-! そ-なのよね-
Translated: <@RL,Lady3,00>Yeah! Exactly!

Original: <@RL,Lady3,00>この間なんかさ- 話しかけたら<CD>何と! わらいかけてくれたの♥
Translated: <@RL,Lady3,00>Can you believe it? When I talked to him the other day, he actually smiled for me~♥

Original: <@RL,Lady3,00>うそ- しんじらんな-い!
Translated: <@RL,Lady3,00>No way! I can't believe that!

Original: <@RL,Man3,00>カラスって 前は<CD>ちかよリがたかったけど<CF><D1>さいきん けっこう 話せるように<CD>なったぜ
Translated: <@RL,Man3,00>Crow used to be so aloof, but he's really easy to talk to nowadays.

Original: <@RL,Lady3,00>貝かけない かおの 子たちに<CD>むリやリ しんけんロボトル<CF><D1>いどまれちゃって<CD>パ-ツ とられまくリ!<CF><D1>3人がかリで 来られちゃ<CD>さすがに ちょっとねぇ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>3人がかリ...?<CD>何か 引っかかるな
Translated: <@RL,Lady3,00>There's a group of three who keep challenging strangers to a serious Robattle and take their Parts! I don't know about that.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>A group of three? That sounds familiar.

Original: <@RL,Lady3,00>マナ-いはんの メダロッタ-は<CD>いただけないわね
Translated: <@RL,Lady3,00>I can't forgive Medarotters without proper etiquette.

Original: <@RL,Man3,00>3人租に いきなリ からまれて<CD>しんけんロボトルで メダロット<CF><D1>丸ごと 持ってかれた<CD>あ-いう わるいことするのは<CF><D1>地上人の やつらだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>3人租...?<CD>ちょっと 気になるな
Translated: <@RL,Man3,00>Three people picked a fight with me out of nowhere and took my whole Medarot after a serious Robattle.<CF><D1>Only surface dwellers would be so ill-behaved.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Three people...? Now I'm worried.

Original: <@RL,Man3,00>オウボウな メダロッタ-は<CD>きらいだ!
Translated: <@RL,Man3,00>I hate tyrannical Medarotters!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>この 学園の子が 言ってた<CD>「3人租」とかいう ことばが<CF><D1>引っかかる<CF><D1>まさかとは 思うけど...
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>Talks about the <f02>three people<f00> that are going rounds in this academy is worrying me.<CF><D1>I really hope it's not them, but...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>カギが かかってる
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>It's locked.

Original: <@RL,Mascot,00>ピ-!
Translated: <@RL,Mascot,00>Pii!

Original: <@RL,Lady,00>うちの ピ-ちゃんは<CD>とっても けなみが いいのよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>「けなみ」??<CF><D1><@RL,Lady,00>ほほ...いいのよ<CD>しろうとには 分からなくて
Translated: <@RL,Lady,00>My Pii's fur is superb!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>"Fur"??<CF><D1><@RL,Lady,00>Hoho... Amateurs won't understand.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>あ! あなたは ハナムラ学園長!<CF><D1><@RL,OldSmiley,00>おお きみか<CF><D1>メダリンピック ゆうしょう<CD>おめでとう!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>知ってたんですか?<CF><D1><@RL,OldSmiley,00>いろんな場所を たびしていれば<CD>しぜんと 耳に 入ってくるよ<CF><D1>これは わたしからの おいわいだ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Ah! You're Headmaster Hanamura!<CF><D1><@RL,OldSmiley,00>Oh, it's you.<CF><D1>Congratulations on winning the Medalympics!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Oh, you knew about it?<CF><D1><@RL,OldSmiley,00>Journeys are tales that travel far and wide.<CF><D1>This is my gift for you!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,01>わあ! あリがとうございます!<CF><D1><@RL,OldSmiley,00>うむ うむ!<CD>これからも がんばるんだぞ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,01>Wow! Thank you so much!<CF><D1><@RL,OldSmiley,00>Mmhmm! Keep up the great work!

Original: <@RL,OldSmiley,00>ここは しずかで いいねぇ
Translated: <@RL,OldSmiley,00>This place is nice and quiet.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>カギが かかってる
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>It's locked.

Original: <@RL,Spyke,01>ちょろいもんすね! あねご<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>イワノイ!?
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,01>That was an easy pick, boss!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>Iwanoi!?

Original: <@RL,Sloan,01>パ-ツ たくさん あつまった♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>カガミヤマ!?
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,01>We got a lot of Parts~♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>Kagamiyama!?

Original: <@RL,Samantha,03>当ったリ前よぉ! あたしたち<CD>スクリュ-ズに かかればさぁ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>キクヒメ!?
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,03>Of course! We're the Screws after all.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>Kikuhime!?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,02>やっぱリそうか!<CF><D1>ライチョウ学園の 子たちに<CD>たかって パ-ツやメダロット<CF><D1>とってるやつらってのは<CD>お前らだな!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,02>I knew it!<CF><D1>You're the ones who took all the Parts and Medarots from the students in Raicho Academy!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,03>あたしたちもぉ けっこう ゆうめいに<CD>なったって ことかしらぁ?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,03>スクリュ-ズの名を せかいじゅうに<CD>ひろめまくるのさ!<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,00>まくるぞ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>...だけど 何で お前ら<CD>こんな所に いるんだよ?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>あたしたちを ほって 月に行ったのは<CD>あんたたちの方でしょぉ?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>そ-だ そ-だ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>えっ それで<CD>ここに いるの?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>わるい-?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,03>いがいと いごこち<CD>いいんだよな ここって<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,01>キレイだし♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,02>だからって すきほうだい<CD>やるなよな!<CF><D1>お前らのせいで ぼくら みんなの<CD>イメ-ジが わるくなるだろ!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>ど-せ ロボトルで<CD>白黒 つけようってんでしょお?<CF><D1>じゃ スカイド-ムで まってるしぃ<CD>かならず 1人で 来なさいよねぇ<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,00>「1人で」だからな!<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,02>カモ-ン!!
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,03>Have we gotten that famous?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,03>The Screws' fame is known throughout the world!<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,00>The world!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>...Why are you guys here anyway?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>You ditched us and went to the moon on your own, you know?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>True that!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Eh? That's why you're here?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>Problem?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,03>This place is actually quite comfortable.<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,01>And pretty~♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,02>That doesn't mean you can just do whatever you want!<CF><D1>You're making our image bad!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>We won those Robattles fair and square, you know?<CF><D1>We'll wait for you at the Sky Dome. Make sure to come alone, okay?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,00><f02>Alone<f00>, okay!?<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,02>Come on!!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>「1人で」と 言われると<CD>おおぜい さそいたくなる
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>If they tell me to come alone, it just makes me want to call the whole gang.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00><&BUF03>
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00><&BUF03>.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>あ! カラス<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>お前が 来てるって<CD>聞いたからな<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>もしかして さがして<CD>くれていたの?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>お前とは もういちどと 言わず<CD>たたかって みたかったしな<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>はかせに 直してもらった<CD>メダロットたちは 元気?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>やつらの ウォ-ミングアップに<CD>いっせん つき合わないか?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Oh, Crow!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>I heard you were coming.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Were you looking for me?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>I want to try Robattling you one more time.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Are the Medarots doing well after professor fixed them?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>Won't you help them warm up with a round?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>ぼくと しょうぶ する前にさ<CD>スカイド-ムに つき合ってよ<CF><D1>カモメちゃんも さそってさ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>But I take you on, come with me to Sky Dome.<CF><D1>You can invite Gull, too!

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>何だ?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>ウォ-ミングアップに ちょうど<CD>いい あいてが いるんだ<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>そうなのか? じゃあ カモメを<CD>よんで スカイド-ムヘ 行っておく
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>What's this about?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>I have a perfect opponent as your warm-up.<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>Is that so? Alright, I'll go to Sky Dome with Gull.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,01>面白く なってきたかも!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,01>Things are getting interesting!

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>やくそく通リ カモメを よんで来たぞ<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>ウォ-ミングアップの あいてって<CD>いうのは どこに いるんだい?
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>As promised, I brought Gull with me.<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>Where are the opponents who will help us warm up?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>そのヘんに いない?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Don't you see them around?

Original: <@RL,Samantha,02>ちょっとぉ ずるいわよぉ!<CD>すけっと つれて 来るなんてぇ!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>聞いてないぞ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,02>お前らに 言えたことかっ!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>しかも よリによって あいては<CD>あの カモメさま!<CF><D1>これは あたしの つらい かこを<CD>たちきる たたかいなのねぇ...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>また わけの 分かんないことを<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>ふっ 何だ お前らか どこかで<CD>貝たと 思ったが<CF><D1>お前らが さいきん この あたリを<CD>あらしてるって 3人租だったのか<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>何よぉ! もんく あるぅ?<CF><D1>目にもの 貝せて やるんだからぁ!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,00>ステ-ジで まってるぜ!
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,02>Wait a second, you're cheating! You're not supposed to call for help!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>You didn't say anything about this!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,02>Like hell I would!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>And of all people, you called my dear Gull! This will be a fight to sever my painful past...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>I don't get what you're talking about.<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>Hmph! No wonder you guys looked familiar. You're the group of three who've been wrecking havoc around here.<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>What! Problem?<CF><D1>I'll show you who's boss!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,00>We'll wait for you on the stage.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>行くぞ カモメ<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>はい 兄さん
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Gull, let's go.<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>Okay, big bro.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,02>ロボトルファイトだ!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>やってやろうじゃなぁい!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>のぞむところだ!<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,02>たとえ ふくが よごれても!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,02>Robattle, fight!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>Let's get this done and over with!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>I've been waiting for this!<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,02>I don't mind if my clothes gets dirty!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,02>ふ-んだ! ちょっと 勝てたからって<CD>い-気に なってんじゃ ないわよぉ
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,02>Hmph! Don't get cocky just because you won this time!

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>お前らに 言いわすれた ことがある<CD>このきかいに 言わせてもらう
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>There's something that I forgot to tell you, so I'll say it now.

Original: <@RL,Samantha,02>な 何よおっ!
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,02>W-what!

Original: <@RL,Spyke,05>あああ あねごに ちかっ<CD>ちかよるなあっ!!
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,05>Aaah! Don't get any closer to our boss!!

Original: <@RL,Crow,01>...あリがとう<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>!!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,05>!?<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,00>??<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>お前らには ずいぶん たすけられた<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>(カラス)<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,01>(兄さん)<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>ロボトル たのしかったぜ<CF><D1>つまらないこと やめて<CD>院を 上げていったら どうだ?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>は はん! えらそ-なこと<CD>言ってんじゃ ね-ぞ!<CF><D1>お前を たすけたのなんて...!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>イワノイ! 行くよ!
Translated: <@RL,Crow,01>...Thank you.<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>!!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,05>!?<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,00>??<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>You guys helped me a bunch.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>(Crow...)<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,01>(Big bro...)<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>It was a fun Robattle.<CF><D1>How about you stop doing stupid things and start honing your skills instead?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>H-hah! Get off your high horse!<CF><D1>We helped you because--<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>Iwanoi! We're leaving!

Original: <@RL,Spyke,00>あねご?
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,00>Boss?

Original: <@RL,Sloan,01>ばいばい
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,01>Bye bye.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>行こう カモメ<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>あ...うん<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00><&BUF03><CD>あとで おれの 家に来い<CF><D1>こんどこそ お前と<CD>しょうぶしたい
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Gull, let's go.<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>Oh... okay.<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00><&BUF03>, come to my house later.<CF><D1>We'll settle our fight there.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>あいつら あれで おとなしく<CD>かえるのかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>I wonder if they'd go home without causing any more problems.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>来たな <&BUF03><CD>となリの ヘやで しょうぶだ
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00><&BUF03>, You're here. We'll Robattle in the next room.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>いくぜ!
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Here I go!

Original: <@RL,Crow,01>たのしかったぜ しょうぶの時は<CD>また 声を かけてくれ
Translated: <@RL,Crow,01>That was fun. Call me whenever you want a fight.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>カラス- ちょっと たのみが<CD>あるんだけど
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>Crow, I need your help with something.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>何だ?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>キクヒメが エアロホテルの ヘやから<CD>出てこなくなったんだ<CF><D1>それで...いっしょに<CD>来てほしいんだけど<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>おれが?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>うん...だめかな?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>エアロホテルだな?<CD>分かった
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>What is it?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Kikuhime is shutting herself in her hotel room.<CF><D1>Well... I want you to come with me to see her.<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>Me?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Yeah... Do you mind?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>Air Hotel, right? Got it.

Original: <@RL,Sloan,03>あねご 出てこない
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,03>Boss won't come out at all.

Original: <@RL,Spyke,04>あねご- あねご-<CD>ヘんじして くださいよ-
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,04>Boss! Boss... Say something...

Original: <@RL,Spyke,04>どうして くれんだよ-<CF><D1>あねご また おかしく<CD>なっちまったじゃね-か!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>ええ? 何で?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>こっちが 聞きたいぜ<CD>あの カラスのやろ-が<CF><D1>あねごの 気にさわること<CD>言ったからじゃね-か!?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>こういうことって 前にも...<CD>キクヒメのヤツ まさか...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>カラスを つれて来るかな
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,04>What happened?<CF><D1>Boss is acting all strange again!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Eeh? Why?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>I want to know myself! Isn't it because she's hurt by what that stupid Crow said!?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Didn't she act like this last time, too? Could it be that Kikuhime is--!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>I'll bring Crow here.

Original: <@RL,Spyke,04>あねご-
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,04>Boss...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>イワノイ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Iwanoi!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>カラスを つれて来た
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>I brought Crow here.

Original: <@RL,Spyke,04>やくに たつのかぁ?
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,04>Is this going to work?

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>キクヒメ 入るぞ<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,05>!!
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Kikuhime, I'm coming in.<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,05>!!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,00>ぐずぐずしてるんじゃ ないわぁ<CD>かえるわよぉ! お前たちぃ!
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,00>This is no time to be dawdling! Guys, we're leaving!

Original: <@RL,Spyke,05>ヘ? あねご?
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,05>Huh? Boss?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>かえっちゃったよ...
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>There they go...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>カラス 何言ったんだ?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>「おれは つよいやつが すきだ<CD>だから 次の メダリンピックでは<CF><D1>だいひょう選手となった お前に<CD>会いたい」って 言った<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>次のメダリンピック? やるの?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>知らん<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>(おいおい...)<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>これで いいんだろう?<CF><D1>おれは 家に もどっている<CD>また ロボトルしよう
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Crow, what did you say to her?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>"I like strong people. I want to see you among the representatives in the next Medalympics."<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Are you going to compete in it?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>No idea.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>(Hey...)<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>I've done my part.<CF><D1>I'm going back home. Let's Robattle again sometime.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>(てきに 回したくない<CD>タイプかも...)
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>(I'd rather not make an enemy out of him...)

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>もんだいの ヘやは どこだ?
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Where's the room in question?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>このかいに あるよ<CD>ついてきて
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>It's on this floor. Follow me.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>どこヘ 行く気だ?
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Where are you going?

Original: <@RL,Boy2,01>兄さん 本当に 変わったよ<CD>何だか 家の中が きゅうに<CF><D1>明るくなった みたいだ<CD><&BUF03>くんの おかげだね<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>そんなこと ないよ<CD>カモメちゃんが いたからさ!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,01>ねえ よければ ぼくとも<CD>ロボトル してくれないかな?<CF><D1>ぼくも 院を上げて 兄さんに<CD>「まいった!」って 言わせたいんだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>あはは! それ 貝てみたいや!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,01>じゃ となリの ヘやヘ 行こう
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,01>Big bro has really changed. Our house suddenly felt so much brighter.<CF><D1><&BUF03>, it's all thanks to you.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>That's not true. It's all you, Gull!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,01>Say, won't you Robattle with me?<CF><D1>I want to get stronger and make big bro call "Uncle!", you see.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Ahaha! I'd love to see that!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,01>Let's go to the next room.

Original: <@RL,Boy2,00>行くよ <&BUF03>くん!
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,00>Here I go, <&BUF03>!

Original: <@RL,Boy2,01>あリがとう <&BUF03>くん<CD>また つきあってくれると うれしいよ
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,01>Thanks, <&BUF03>. It'd make me happy if we can do this again sometime.

Original: <@RL,Boy2,01>また あいてを してくれるんだね?
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,01>You're here to fight me again, right?

Original: <@RL,Boy2,00>手かげんは いらないよ!
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,00>No need to hold back!

Original: <@RL,Crow,01>あリがとう たのしかったよ<CD>また つきあってくれるかい?
Translated: <@RL,Crow,01>Thanks, that was fun. Will you come again?

Original: <@RL,Spyke,03>お? ロボトルか?<CD>うけて立ってやるぜ!
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,03>Oh, a Robattle? I'll take on your challenge!

Original: <@RL,Spyke,02>あねごの ために<CD>おれは たたかい...<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,04>つかれた...かも
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,02>I fight for boss' sake...<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,04>But... I might have gotten tired.

Original: <@RL,Sloan,00>ぼくだって たくさん<CD>パ-ツが ほしい!
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,00>I want to have lots of Parts!

Original: <@RL,Sloan,01>ピッカピカの キレイな<CD>パ-ツ ほしいなぁ♥
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,01>I want those sparkling, beautiful Parts~♥

Original: <@RL,Samantha,02>あんたなんかにぃ いつまでも<CD>大きなかお させないんだからぁ!
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,02>I won't let you hog all the glory forever!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,02>あんたに まけたらぁ カラスさまに<CD>かおむけ できないじゃなぁい!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>(なんだかな-)
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,02>If I lose against you, I won't be able to face my dear Crow anymore!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>(I wonder...)

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>あ! ヒカルさん<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,01>やあ <&BUF03>くん<CD>何を おどろいているんだい?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>だ だって<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,00>ここに いちゃ おかしいかい?<CD>ここは ぼくの ヘやだよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>レアメダルは...?<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,01>もう はかせに わたしたよ<CF><D1>とリあえず このあたリに ほかの<CD>レアメダルは ないみたいだしね<CF><D1>しばらく レトルトは きゅうぎょうだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>そうなんですか...<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,01>じゃ ぼくは バイトに 行くよ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Oh, Hikaru!<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,01>Hey, <&BUF03>. Why do you look so surprised?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>I-I mean...<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,00>Is it strange for me to be here? This is my room, you know?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>What about the rare Medal...?<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,01>I already gave it to the professor.<CF><D1>I think there are no more rare medals in this area.<CF><D1>Phantom Retort is having a vacation for a while.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>I see...<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,01>See you, I'm going to my part-time job.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ヒカルさん 学校 行ってるのかな?<CD>...人のこと 言えないけど
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Hikaru, does he ever go to school? ...Not that I'm one to say.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>こんにちは だいじんさん<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>おお <&BUF03>くんか<CD>まっておったよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>え? ぼくを ですか?<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>ぜひとも きみに<CD>たのみたいことが あってな<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>? 何ですか?<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>もういちど 宇宙ヘ 行く気は<CD>ないか?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Good afternoon, prime minister.<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>Oh, <&BUF03>. I was waiting for you.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Eh? You were?<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>There's something I need your help with.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>? What is it?<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>Do you want to go to space one more time?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>えっ!?<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>きみに 宇宙ロボトルに おける<CD>モニタ-と なってほしいんだ<CF><D1>まだまだ 宇宙フィ-ルドでの<CD>ロボトルデ-タは ふそくして<CF><D1>おるからな<CF><D1>きみが ロボトルした デ-タは<CD>ちょくせつ ヘブンスゲ-トの<CF><D1>メダロット社に<CD>おくられることに なる<CF><D1>きみは ユウキくんの たっての<CD>すいせんだ<CF><D1>どうだ? やってくれるか?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>は...はい! よろこんで!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>うむ きみなら そう言ってくれると<CD>しんじていたぞ<CF><D1>では これを うけとるがいい
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Eh!?<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>I want you to be our tester in space Robattles.<CF><D1>Data on Space field Robattles are very lacking after all.<CF><D1>Data from your Robattles will be sent directly to the Medarot Corporation at Heaven's Gate.<CF><D1>Even Yuki is vouching for you.<CF><D1>What do you think? Will you do it for me?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Y-yes... With pleasure!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>Mmhmm, I believed you of all people would say yes.<CF><D1>Take this with you.

Original: <@RL,Man,00>わたしの サインの 入った<CD>この チケットさえ あれば<CF><D1>なんどでも 宇宙ヘ<CD>とぶことが できる<CF><D1>では たのんだぞ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>は はいっ!!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>うむ うむ<CF><D1>それと 3Fの パ-ツも 使って<CD>くれたまえ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>わかリました!
Translated: <@RL,Man,00>This ticket has my signature on it. You can use it to fly to space anytime you want.<CF><D1>I'm counting on you.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Y-yes, sir!!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>Mmhmm.<CF><D1>Also, you can use the Parts on 3F.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Understood!

Original: <@RL,Man,00>カラスや カモメにも きみのような<CD>友だちが できて なによリだ<CF><D1>これからも なかよくしてやってくれ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>はい!
Translated: <@RL,Man,00>I'm glad Crow and Gull could be friends with you.<CF><D1>Please get along with them.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Yes, sir!

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>そうリには くれぐれも<CD>そそうの ないように!
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Don't let the prime minister down!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>ひ--っ!! 宇宙ステ-ション<CD>「ランデブ-」おうふくチケット<CF><D1>6000000¥!?<CF><D1>宇宙に 1回 行くだけで<CD>そんなに するのぉ!?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Hiiih!! A round trip to Space Station <f02>Rendezvous<f00> costs ¥6,000,000!?<CF><D1>That's how much you need to pay just to go to space once!?

Original: <@RL,Clerk,00>こちらの スタ-ゲ-トからは<CD>宇宙ステ-ション<CF><D1>「ランデブ-」行きの シャトルに<CD>ごとうじょう できます
Translated: <@RL,Clerk,00>This Star Gate leads to the shuttle bound for <f02>Rendezvous<f00>.

Original: <@RL,Clerk,00>もうしわけ ございませんが<CD>チケットを お持ちでない<CF><D1>おきゃくさまは お通し できません
Translated: <@RL,Clerk,00>I'm sorry, sir. You need a ticket to proceed.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,03>そうだよね- 宇宙って いうのは<CD>そう なんども 行けるもんじゃ<CF><D1>ないよね-
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,03>You're right, space is not somewhere people can go willy-nilly.

Original: <@RL,Clerk,00>チケットを はいけん いたします
Translated: <@RL,Clerk,00>I'm checking your ticket.

Original: <@RL,Clerk,00>...はい! かくにんしました<CD>星空の たびを おたのしみ ください
Translated: <@RL,Clerk,00>...! I've confirmed your ticket. Please enjoy your trip to the starry sky.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ちきゅうに かえる?<*04>
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Should I go back to Earth?<*04>

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ビ-ハイブに 行く?<*04>
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Should I go to Beehive?<*04>

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ランデブ-に 行く?<*04>
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Should I go to Rendezvous?<*04>

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ここを 下リれば 月の海だ<CD>月の海ヘ 行く?<*04>
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Lunar Mare is just below here. Should I go to Lunar Mare?<*04>

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>ここは 宇宙ふくが いらないから<CD>ぬいでおこう
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>I don't need a spacesuit here. I'll take it off.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>やっぱリ やめとこ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Maybe not.

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>ボクは ここに すみついちゃった<CD>メダロット<CF><D1>キミが 「はい」って 言うなら<CD>外に つれてって あげるヨ?<*04>
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>I'm a Medarot that has settled down here.<CF><D1>Do you want to go outside? Choose "Yes" if you do.<*04>

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>よォし! 行くゾォ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>ちょっと まって!<CD>きがえなきゃ!
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>Alright! Let's go!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Hold on! I need to change first!

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>まったね-!
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>See you again!

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>...あれ? いいのォ?
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>...Huh? Are you sure?

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>ねえねえ お外 行きたい?<CD>行きたい? ねえねえ!<*04>
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>Say, say, wanna go outside? Wanna go? Say, say!<*04>

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>ボクも 行きたい!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>ちょっと まって!<CD>きがえなきゃ!
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>I wanna go, too!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Hold on! I need to change first!

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>またね またね またね!
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>Bye bye bye!

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>...ボクは キミと 行きたかった!
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>...I wanted to go with you!

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>そろそろ 外が<CD>こいしくなってきた?<*04>
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>Have you started to miss the outside?<*04>

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>じゃあ つれてって あげよう<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>ちょっと まって!<CD>きがえなきゃ!
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>Alright, I'll take you there.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Hold on! I need to change first!

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>ボクが こいしくなったら<CD>もどって おいで
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>Come back here if you start to miss me.

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>...本当に?
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>...Really?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>このUFOって ブラックデビルが<CD>ねむってたんだよね<CF><D1>ミニミニマシ-ンも ここに<CD>あったのかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>This UFO is where Black Devil was sleeping, right?<CF><D1>I wonder if the Mini-mini Machine was also found here.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>...って ことは ほかにも<CD>何か のこってるかも
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>...I might be able to find something else.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>このコンピュ-タ 気になる...<CD>もういちど しらベて みようかな
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>This computer is getting my curious... I should examine it one more time.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00><&BUF07>!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00><&BUF07>!

Original: <@RL,Metabee,00>あ-?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>おねがいが あるんだ<CF><D1>また このコンピュ-タに<CD>はまって くれないかな?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>すきじゃ ね-んだよな<CD>そこに 入んの<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>...ダメ?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>...1回だけだぜ?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>うん!
Translated: <@RL,Metabee,00>Aah?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>I need your help.<CF><D1>Do you mind plugging into this computer one more time?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>I don't really like getting into that, you know?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>...Is that a no?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>...Just once, okay?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Mmhmm!

Original: <@RL,Rokusho,00>何だ?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>おねがいが あるんだ<CF><D1>また このコンピュ-タに<CD>はまって くれないかな?<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>気に食わんな<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>...ダメ?<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>...1回だけだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>うん!
Translated: <@RL,Rokusho,00>What?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>I need your help.<CF><D1>Do you mind plugging into this computer one more time?<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>I don't like it one bit.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>...Is that a no??<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>...Just once.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Mmhmm!

Original: <@RL,Metabee,00>キ-ワ-ドを のベよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>じゃ とリあえず<CD>「ミニミニマシ-ン」の ことでも<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>ミニミニマシ-ンは<CD>アイテムごうせいで 生まれたもの<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>アイテムごうせい?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>アイテムを とうにゅうせよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>アイテム? 何でも いいのかな?<CD>じゃ「風のつばさ」を 入れよう
Translated: <@RL,Metabee,00>State your keyword.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Let's start with "Mini-mini Machine".<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>The Mini-mini Machine was born from an item synthesis.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Item synthesis?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>Insert an item.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>An item? Will any item do? Let me try putting in <f02>Wings of Wind<f00>.

Original: <@RL,Rokusho,00>キ-ワ-ドを のベよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>じゃ とリあえず<CD>「ミニミニマシ-ン」の ことでも<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>ミニミニマシ-ンは<CD>アイテムごうせいで 生まれたもの<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>アイテムごうせい?<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>アイテムを とうにゅうせよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>アイテム? 何でも いいのかな?<CD>じゃ「風のつばさ」を 入れよう
Translated: <@RL,Rokusho,00>State your keyword.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Let's start with "Mini-mini Machine".<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>The Mini-mini Machine was born from an item synthesis.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Item synthesis?<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>Insert an item.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>An item? Will any item do? Let me try putting in <f02>Wings of Wind<f00>.

Original: <@RL,Metabee,00>ごうせいする アイテムを<CD>とうにゅうせよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>? よく分からないけど<CD>てきとうに「タウンマップ」でも
Translated: <@RL,Metabee,00>Insert an item to synthesis it with.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>? I don't really get it. I'll just put in <f02>Town Map<f00> or something.

Original: <@RL,Rokusho,00>ごうせいする アイテムを<CD>とうにゅうせよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>? よく分からないけど<CD>てきとうに「タウンマップ」でも
Translated: <@RL,Rokusho,00>Insert an item to synthesis it with.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>? I don't really get it. I'll just put in <f02>Town Map<f00> or something.

Original: <@RL,Metabee,00>アイテム名「風のつばさ」に<CD>「テレポ-タ-」きのう ついか<CF><D1>...って もう いいだろ?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>ああ ごめんごめん<CD>あリがとう
Translated: <@RL,Metabee,00>Item name: <f02>Wings of Wind<f00> is now added with a new feature, <f02>Teleporter<f00>.<CF><D1>...Hey, isn't that enough?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Yeah, sorry about that. Thanks.

Original: <@RL,Rokusho,00>アイテム名「風のつばさ」に<CD>「テレポ-タ-」きのう ついか<CF><D1>...もう いいだろう?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>ああ ごめんごめん<CD>あリがとう
Translated: <@RL,Rokusho,00>Item name: <f02>Wings of Wind<f00> is now added with a new feature, <f02>Teleporter<f00>.<CF><D1>...Isn't that enough?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Yeah, sorry about that. Thanks.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ところでさ テレポ-タ-きのうって<CD>何なわけ?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>風のつばさは しゅんかんいどう<CD>できるように なったのさ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>ヘ-っ ベんリ!<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>言っとくけどなぁ オレは<CD>にどと ごめんだぞ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>By the way, what does Teleporter do?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>Now you can go to another place instantly with Wings of Wind.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>Wow, that's really useful!<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>Let me say this first, I'm not doing that anymore!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ところでさ テレポ-タ-きのうって<CD>何なわけ?<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>風のつばさは しゅんかんいどう<CD>できるように なった<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>ヘ-っ ベんリ!<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>言っておくが おれは にどと<CD>ごめんだ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>By the way, what does Teleporter do?<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>You can now go to another place instantly with Wings of Wind.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>Wow, that's really useful!<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>Let me say this, I'm not doing that a second time.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>分かった 分かった<CD>もう たのまないからさ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Okay, I heard you. I'm not gonna make you do that anymore.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>このコンピュ-タには ほかに<CD>どんな デ-タが つまってるのかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>What other data does this computer have?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>何だ? これ なになに?<CD>「快盗レトルト さんじょう!」
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Huh? What's this? "Phantom Retort has arrived!"

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>...って うっそ-!<CD>レトルトさん こんな所まで!?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>ぼくが UFOの 話したの<CD>はかせだけだし<CF><D1>この場所 はかせに<CD>聞いたのかな?<CF><D1>だとすれば レトルトさんの<CD>ねらいは...
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>...Huh? No way! Phantom Retort is coming all the way here!?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>I only talked about the UFO with the professor.<CF><D1>Did the professor tell him about this place?<CF><D1>In that case, Phantom Retort's objective would be...

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>ふははははははは!
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>Fuahahahahahahaha!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>あの声は レトルトさん!<CD>ここに レトルトさんが!!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>レトルトレディも!<CF><D1>それに...1番上にいる<CD>メダロットって ブラックカブト!<CF><D1>それから...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>レトルトレディも!<CF><D1>それに...1番上にいる<CD>メダロットって ブラッククワガタ!<CF><D1>それから...

Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>I found a rare Medal!<CF><D1><@RL,LadyRenegade,01>You're not getting away!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>レアメダル!?<CD>じゃあ やっぱリ...<CF><D1><@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>ウウウウウ...<CF><D1><@RL,LadyRenegade,01>あ-ら こわがらなくって いいのよぉ<CF><D1>おとなしく していれば<CD>すぐ おわるんだから♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>(レトルトレディ...<CD>その 言い方は ちょっと)<CF><D1><@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>グウウウウ...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>レトルトさん! レトルトレディ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>A rare Medal!? I knew it...<CF><D1><@RL,FlyingMedabot,00><f03>Uuuuu<f00>...<CF><D1><@RL,LadyRenegade,01>My, no need to be scared.<CF><D1>Be still and it'll be over in no time~♥<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>(Lady Retort... You could've picked your words more.)<CF><D1><@RL,FlyingMedabot,00><f03>Guuuuu<f00>...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>Phantom Retort! Lady Retort!

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,00><&BUF03>くん!<CF><D1><@RL,LadyRenegade,01>あら また 会えたわね♥
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,00><&BUF03>!<CF><D1><@RL,LadyRenegade,01>My, we meet again~♥

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>やっぱリ ブラックカブト!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>I knew it, it's Black Kabuto!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>やっぱリ ブラッククワガタ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>I knew it, it's Black Kuwagata!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>それから ブラックデビルの<CD>メダロットたち!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ブラックカブトが ほかにも<CD>いたなんて...<CF><D1><@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>わたしたちは ブラックデビルさまの<CD>めいれいしか きかない!<CF><D1>しんにゅう者は たおす!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>ブラックデビルは もう<CD>かえったんだよ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>I didn't expect there would be more than one Black Kabuto...<CF><D1><@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>We only listen to Black Devil's orders and no one else's!<CF><D1>Intruders will go down!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Black Devil has gone home!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ブラッククワガタが ほかにも<CD>いたなんて...<CF><D1><@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>わたしたちは ブラックデビルさまの<CD>めいれいしか きかない!<CF><D1>しんにゅう者は たおす!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>ブラックデビルは もう<CD>かえったんだよ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>I didn't expect there would be more than one Black Kuwagata...<CF><D1><@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>We only listen to Black Devil's orders and no one else's!<CF><D1>Intruders will go down!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Black Devil has gone home!

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>ブラックデビル...<CD>はかせから 聞いたよ<CF><D1>レアメダルを うみ出す 力を 持った<CD>メダロットだってこと<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>レトルトさんたち...やっぱリ<CD>はかせから ぼくの 話を 聞いて<CF><D1>ここに 来たんですね<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>その通リだ <&BUF03>くん<CF><D1>わたしの しめいを 知ったからには<CD>きみにも きょうリょく してもらうよ
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>Black Devil... I heard from the professor.<CF><D1>He's a Medarot that has the power to give birth to rare Medals.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Phantom Retort, Lady Retort... So you're here because he told you about me.<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>Exactly, <&BUF03>.<CF><D1>Since you know what my mission is, I'd like you to give me a hand.

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>こちらとしても その<CD>ブラックデビルとやらが 作った<CF><D1>レアメダルの じつリょくを<CD>貝てみたい
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>As for me, I want to see how strong the rare Medals that Black Devil made.

Original: <@RL,LadyRenegade,01>そ-ゆ-こと!

Original: <@RL,LadyRenegade,01>行くわよ!<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>おお!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>ええ!?
Translated: <@RL,LadyRenegade,01>Here I go!<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>Yeah!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>Huh!?

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>そこを どいて!<CD><&BUF03>くん!
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>Make way, <&BUF03>!

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>メダルハンタ- 快盗レトルト!<CD>カレ-に レアメダルを ゲット!
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>Phantom Retort, the Medal Hunter has obtained a rare Medal with elegance!

Original: <@RL,LadyRenegade,02>もしかして はつ白星じゃない?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>.........

Original: <@RL,LadyRenegade,03>あっ! まちなさいっ!

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,03>にがすかっ!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>あ! まって!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>レトルトさんたち どこ<CD>行っちゃったんだろ<CF><D1>早く おいかけよう!

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>ふはははは!
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,01>Fuahahahaha!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>レトルトさんの 声だ!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>レトルトさん! レトルトレディ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Phantom Retort! Lady Retort!

Original: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>やっぱリ 来てくれたんだね<CD><&BUF03>くん<CF><D1><@RL,LadyRenegade,01>いらっしゃ-い♥
Translated: <@RL,PhantomRenegade,00>I knew you would come, <&BUF03>.<CF><D1><@RL,LadyRenegade,01>Hey there~♥
